Arcane Door		KEY:Arcane Door ~ Arcane Juggler	CATEGORY:Special Ability	SOURCEPAGE:p.83	TYPE:SpecialQuality.SpellLike				DESC: While using the arcane juggle, the arcane juggler is able to step into the loop of juggled items and enter a dimension door. All the juggled items remain where he was, and do not teleport to his new location. An arcane door can only be created while an arcane juggle is in effect. The items may be anything-even as mundane an item as pebbles- but they must number 6 items total. An arcane juggler may call up a number of arcane doors per day equal to his Charisma modifi er, and may not take anyone with him unless they are actually attached to his body. The effects of the arcane door is similar to that of a dimension door spell, except that the distance available to the arcane juggler is less; only 200 ft. + 20 ft. per arcane juggler level.

