Pack Bonding (Su): Pack bonding provides the wereranger with the ability to use clairvoyance and clairaudience (as per the spells of the same name) with the animals of his pack. With this ability, he may see through the eyes of one of his followers or hear through their ears up to a maximum range of 3 miles from the target animal. Furthermore, the wereranger gains the racial bonus of those skills that he shares with the animals in his pack at all times. For example, a wereranger with the Move Silently skill and who has 6 rats in his animal pack will gain a +4 racial bonus to his Move Silently skill checks. Note that if the wereranger has more than one animal type in his pack with the same skill bonuses, the racial bonuses do not stack. Additionally, he must have ranks of his own in the skill in order to receive the bonus from his animal allies. If any animal dies or leaves the pack, the wereranger loses the racial bonus from that animal.
