Nature's Spirit (Su): Once per day the wereranger may completely transform into a dire version of a predetermined animal (chosen when he gains this ability). The transformation is complete, and the wereranger's type changes to that of Animal, and he gains the best ability scores and skill bonuses available to him from his own scores or that of the dire animal.

